title: VoxFeed - La app gratuita de Influencer Marketing
description: VoxFeed is the app that rewards you for recommending your favorite brands in your social network accounts. To participate, you only need to register and link your accounts. Once registered, you will be able to participate in the campaigns of the brands you like the most and earn money by posting in your social networks. You will receive your money in a PayPal or Payoneer account
